text: Jáchym Bulín (born 7 September 1934) is a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
